snippet: The police were summoned to the town of Wallenfels after a woman called an emergency doctor to say that she had discovered what appeared to be body parts.

byline.contributor: Claire Barthelemy contributed reporting from London, and Katarina Johannsen from Berlin.

lead_paragraph: The police were summoned to the town of Wallenfels after a woman called an emergency doctor to say that she had discovered what appeared to be body parts.

headline.main: Remains of Babies Are Found in Bavaria
